/*This is a new concept that you must know in order to protect yourself of malicious cyber criminals*/
Social Engineering
Social engineering works by manipulating normal human
behavioural traits and as such there are only limited technical solutions to guard against it. As a result,
the best defence is to educate users on the techniques used by social engineers, and raising awareness
as to how both humans and computer systems can be manipulated to create a false level of trust.

